Interface IManagedType

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
CollectionValuedFieldResolver.MapManagedType, FromSubqueryResolver.VirtualManagedType, StateFieldPathExpressionStateObject.MapManagedType
public interface IManagedType extends Comparable<IManagedType>
The external representation of a managed type, which is a JPA persistent object.

Provisional API: This interface is part of an interim API that is still under development and expected to change significantly before reaching stability. It is available at this early stage to solicit feedback from pioneering adopters on the understanding that any code that uses this API will almost certainly be broken (repeatedly) as the API evolves.
